txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Jellied goo from the insects and spiders north of Oatbarton. You can make the delivery to Ponto Oats at Oatbarton centre.
'I am certain that we will be able to find a use for these.'
'If you happen upon any of the tougher types of insects to the north be sure to collect everything from them, I am certain that we can find a use for most everything that you find from them.'
The townsfolk in Oatbarton await the delivery of jellied goo to Ponto Oats at the centre of the town.
Deliver the jellied goo to Ponto Oats at Oatbarton
You have been tasked with collecting and delivering jellied goo from the insects and spiders north of Oatbarton. You are to deliver the items to Ponto Oats at the centre of the town of Oatbarton.
Wanted: Jellied goo from the insects and spiders north of Oatbarton.
